      <title>斯里兰卡大选前几天达成重组协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/sri-lanka-says-restructuring-deal-with-bondholders-reached</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡表示，在该国即将举行令投资者感到不安的大选前两天，该国已与债券持有人达成原则协议，将重组约 126 亿美元的债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/sri-lanka-says-restructuring-deal-with-bondholders-reached</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 10:34:46 GMT</pubDate>
